            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "That's...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sis! You really did come for me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yup. Nio, you did a good job hanging in there till now. Let's go back to the workshop together...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I can't... The person beyond this point is really mad."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "He won't let me out...ever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "And he'll eliminate anyone who tries to stop him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "If it's just for a short while, I think I can hold him back. So Sis..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Run away from here. I'll be fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It's enough that you came to this place for me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry. I absolutely will get you out of here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Well, we did receive that warning."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I will proceed and settle this in my own way, but...what will you do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'll...save Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "In that case, the path we must travel is one and the same. A frontal breach it shall be."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yes, let's go!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "No matter what happens, I'm taking Nio back with me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Nio, I'll be there soon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "So, wait for me...!"
        }
    ]
}